Hungary to Fire 1,000 State Media Staff, Nepszabadsag Reports

-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 
2011-05-11T06:04:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-11/hungary-to-fire-1-000-state-media-staff-nepszabadsag-reports.html
Hungary plans to fire 1,000 people
from state media companies this year,  Nepszabadsag  reported,
today, citing a letter asking editors-in-chief to present plans
by Monday detailing which jobs they plan to cut.  The jobs will be cut in two rounds of 500 each, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andras Gergely in Budapest 
 agergely@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Kirkland in  London  at 
 skirkland@bloomberg.net . 